{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72/events","html_url":"https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72","id":396848679,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzOTY4NDg2Nzk=","number":72,"title":"different width/height offset learning compared with darknet?","user":{"login":"muye5","id":1658029,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2NTgwMjk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1658029?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5","html_url":"https://github.com/muye5","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":21,"created_at":"2019-01-08T10:44:52Z","updated_at":"2019-04-23T15:06:28Z","closed_at":"2019-01-09T11:03:02Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"I noticed the log transformation of w/h offset in this repo was different from darknet as my understanding.\r\n[utils/build_targets @Line 227](https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov3/blob/master/utils/utils.py)\r\n`TC[b, :nTb], gx, gy, gw, gh = t[:, 0].long(), t[:, 1] * nG, t[:, 2] * nG, t[:, 3] * nG, t[:, 4] * nG`\r\nhere, `xy` and `wh` are all relative to grid e.g.(input=416, grid=13/26/52), so as to `anchor * exp(t_w)`\r\nbut in darknet, `xy` are relative to grid, `wh` are relative to input as my understanding, `anchor * exp(t_w)` doesn't need to scale.\r\n[yolo_layer.c @Line 88](https://github.com/pjreddie/darknet/blob/master/src/yolo_layer.c)\r\n`b.w = exp(x[index + 2*stride]) * biases[2*n]   / w;`\r\n\r\nso if predicting with the weight file provided by the author, I think this will cause some mistakes.\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"muye5","id":1658029,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2NTgwMjk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1658029?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5","html_url":"https://github.com/muye5","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muye5/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ultralytics/yolov3/issues/72/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}